c: 61
v: 5
t: "Yoh dilee Musa teuma geupeugah Geukheun bak Tuhan geuh hai kawom lon , Pakon ateuh lon tapeugot susah ‘ Gata dum tapeusaket ate lon Ka tateupeue lon nyoe rasul Allah Peurintah Tuhan lon ba bak gata ‘Oh ban ka nyata jih sisat leupah Tuhan peusisat treuk ate jih nyan Nyata treuk jih nyan awak nyang salah Han Neupeutunyok teuma di Tuhan Barangri kawom nyang pasek leupah"